description:
Finally was able to try the Gingersnaps featured on the 2011 SF 7x7 List. 

// LOCATION // Ferry Building next to Humphry Slocombe

// SERVICE // The shop is adorable and the employee was very sweet. Accepts credit cards using the Square App on their iPad

// FOOD // 
     + Gingersnaps: Thicker than your standard gingersnap. The ginger flavor is very strong that leaves your mouth feeling cool and refreshed. It is not too sweet which I loved. 
     + Macarons: Did not try them so cannot speak to their flavor, but they looked dull in color and lackluster. 

The Gingersnaps are worth a try and packaged in a cute cylinder little container which makes traveling with them a breeze!
